            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/reviews/stats",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "reviews", "stats"]
            },
            "description": "Get dashboard statistics for authenticated user's reviews.\n\n**Authentication Required:** JWT Bearer token\n\n**Returns:**\n- totalReviews: Total number of reviews\n- positiveCount, neutralCount, negativeCount: Sentiment breakdown\n- positivePercent, neutralPercent, negativePercent: Percentages\n- topThemes: Array of themes with percentages"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Create New Review (Protected)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status code is 201', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Reviews were created', function() {",
                  "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.be.an('array');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.length).to.be.greaterThan(0);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{jwt_token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"text\": \"The service was excellent and staff were very helpful\\nThe room was clean and comfortable\\nLocation was perfect for our needs\",\n  \"tone\": \"Professional\",\n  \"language\": \"English\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/reviews",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "reviews"]
            },
            "description": "Analyze and create reviews from text input.\n\n**Authentication Required:** JWT Bearer token\n\n**Request Body:**\n- text: Multi-line review text (one review per line)\n- tone: Response tone (Professional, Casual, Empathetic, Concise)\n- language: Response language (English, Spanish, French, German)\n\n**AI Processing:**\n- Sentiment analysis (Positive/Negative/Neutral)\n- Theme classification\n- Suggested response generation"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
